title: Blueberry Streusel Muffins
ingredients: ['165g plain flour', '5 tablespoons caster sugar', '70g dark brown soft sugar', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '75ml vegetable oil', '2 eggs', '125ml milk', '220g blueberries', '5 tablespoons plain flour', '50g butter, softened', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '50g dark brown soft sugar']
